b'6/16
I see massive potential in Web3 and NFTs and keep exploring them. I am unsure where this will lead me, but I want to continue to learn.

Here is an overview of all entries, each in a separate post:'

b"5/16\nThat's why I got into a few NFT projects, especially into @RTFKT after they were acquired by @Nike. @Nike is a long-time partner of mine, so that felt like a natural fit. Web3 is very much about community, and I see @RTFKT having a strong one. #rtfktcreators"

b'4/16\nBut let me explain why I am doing this at all. So many people reach out to me to convince me to participate in their NFT projects or do some NFTs for me. At the end of last year, this triggered me to learn more about NFTs. I only do things that I am 100% convinced of.'

b'3/16\nI will surely use one of them as my PFP \xe2\x80\x93 or might even change them occasionally. But, deep down, I know there is much more potential in these 3D Avatars than just using them as a PFP.'

b'2/16 \xf0\x9f\x91\x86\xf0\x9f\x91\x86They sent over their work. All with different aesthetics but on a high level of execution. (Added all the submissions below). Thanks so much. Of course, I will send everyone a signed jersey.'
